msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 18 (plate)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 153 (18d8 + 72)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft., fly 60 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR      | DEX     | CON      | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|----------|---------|----------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 18 (+4) | 16 (+3) | 18 (+4) | 14 (+2) | 14 (+2) | 18 (+4) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Saving Throws** Dex +7, Con +8, Wis +6, Cha +8    \n"
"**Damage Resistances** cold; bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from "
"nonmagical attacks that aren't silvered    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** fire, poison    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** poisoned    \n"
"**Senses** truesight 120 ft., passive Perception 12    \n"
"**Languages** Infernal, telepathy 120 ft.    \n"
"**Challenge** 12 (8,400 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Hellish Weapons.** The erinyes's weapon attacks are magical and deal an "
"extra 13 (3d8) poison damage on a hit (included in the attacks).    \n"
"**Magic Resistance.** The erinyes has advantage on saving throws against "
"spells and other magical effects. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The erinyes makes three attacks.    \n"
"**Longsword.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +8 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 8 (1d8 + 4) slashing damage, or 9 (1d10 + 4) slashing damage "
"if used with two hands, plus 13 (3d8) poison damage.    \n"
"**Longbow.** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, range 150/600 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage plus 13 (3d8) poison damage, and "
"the target must succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or be "
"poisoned. The poison lasts until it is removed by the lesser restoration "
"spell or similar magic. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/erinyes.md:33
msgid ""
"### Reactions **Parry.** The erinyes adds 4 to its AC against one melee "
"attack that would hit it. To do so, the erinyes must see the attacker and be "
"wielding a melee weapon."
msgstr ""
